name: Fallen Queen I: Bile
description: @AledinArt | "Fallen Queen I: Bile" is one of the 3 pieces "Fallen Queens" collection by Alejandro Dini, the other two being "Fallen Queen II: Sorrow" and "Fallen Queen III:Grudge". They represent dark emotional states towering over reason, as they appear in famous ancient folk tales often embodied by witches.
